    "name": "REQ-NAGARAJA-001: Acceptance bounds for FEA compression-bending prediction",
    "description": "All three quantities of interest (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) shall be predicted within 10% of the experimental mean across both laboratories. The normalised validation metric E/uval shall remain below 1.96 for each QoI. Model risk level 3 requires minimum credibility factor gradation of 2 for all computational factors and 3 for validation factors.",
    "source": "Internal V&V Plan VVP-2023-NC-001, Rev B"
